# Definition of Done

For any substantial feature, fix, or refactor, completion requires:

- code implementation is complete and coherent
- tests are added/updated for changed behavior
- docs are updated when behavior/workflow changes
- changelog/release notes are updated when the project uses them
- project quality checks pass (lint, typecheck, test, build)

## Final handoff should include

- what changed
- validation commands run and outcomes
- known limitations or follow-ups
- rollback/risk note for impactful changes
